ge=EN>Salicia Swiftfoot</A> at: 11/12/01 5:54:00 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulyberniabelisama.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lybernia Belisama</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.sherilyn.net/misc/sherry.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(11/12/01 6:00:30 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.sherilyn.net/sigs/lyb2.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /sticky is just about useless now - /face isn't much bet</span><hr size=1> I agree, they made the range for /stick to low.  I can be standing within throwing distance of the mob and still can't /stick.  <br>
<br>
<img src=http://www.sherilyn.net/sigs/faptila.jpg> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulyberniabelisama.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lybernia Belisama</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.sherilyn.net/misc/sherry.gif" BORDER=0> at: 11/12/01 6:00:47 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uerindathsurefoot.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Erindath Surefoot</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(11/12/01 6:03:33 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.home.net/bjcabe/emblem.jpg hiegth=125 width=56></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: /sticky is just about useless now - /face isn't much bet</span><hr size=1> Bleh i was never a fan of /stick when they put it in back in beta when i was playing my Champ =(<br>
<br>
IMO it really takes away from the dancing and tactics a tank can use against another tank. With /stick you might as well just stand there and trade blows with each other. *shrugs* I see RvR between tanks as an art form, some will be better then others and you cant really express your art when you cant shake someone off your arse.  <p><table>
